Guitar.create(name: "Beard Guitars Deco Phonic Sidecar Acoustic Guitar Satin Tobacco Sunburst", description: "The Sidecar from Beard Guitars is the flagship model of the Deco line. The classic and compact Beard ‚ÄúR‚Äù body shape is comfortable and appealing, with a solid spruce top featuring mahogany Aero bracing to provide a rich, balanced sound and a slightly pronounced midrange response. The Sidecar is especially suited for fingerstyle and blues. An incredibly subtle soft V-shape mahogany neck and 14 fret range provide plenty of comfort and access.", price: 2200.00, image_url: "https://media.guitarcenter.com/is/image/MMGS7/L84964000001000-00-720x720.jpg")

